THE LIGHTHOUSE ★★★☆☆
Technically adroit. However, story and dénouement underwhelm. Madness and isolation has been done far better, e.g. THE SHINING, THE OTHERS. For a closer, superior film, check out HOW I ENDED THIS SUMMER.
